{
  "stem": "4695.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they know they are-- they know all over the world what is cooking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If that's true, then you must have had some idea of what was happening in Germany and the rise of Nazism.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, partly we know what will be happened when we read Or in Germany, or in-- even in the translation in Polish, you see what is-- what will be.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But mostly people, even doctors, engineers, said, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This can never be happened because this is the 20th century.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Germany is a nation from culture and civilization.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This will never be.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is not 300, 400 years ago.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, don't believe that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It is only for domestic propaganda, but not-- will never be this in practice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I feel it in my blood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know the German history, and I know was-- that this will be happened, in-- but you cannot help.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are alone or a small group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what is to do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I like to emigrate, but nowhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every-- the border are closed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell to my wife, let's go out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even before we married, I tell her I like to [INAUDIBLE] from Belgium to the states.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't like this territory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Here there will be-- how is that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[POLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The health-- the hell will be here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in [INAUDIBLE] that they-- pogroms even in Poland in the-- in the propaganda.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It comes closer and closer, you see, to, to press on the Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I understand that not only that, then Hitler not only then, he like to liquidate the Jewish people as a whole.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he like with the Jewish people to use as the Greek was using the Trojans'-- the Trojans' horses.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
